{"id":68812,"title":"Hypertension in hemodialysis patients: an opinion-based update.","abstract":"Hypertension is highly prevalent in hemodialysis patients but its management remains a matter of debate. In this review, we discuss the observational studies on the association of blood pressure with outcomes, measurement of blood pressure in hemodialysis patients and present an opinion-based approach to treating hypertension. ","date":"2014-03-04","categories":"Male Urogenital Diseases","split":"test","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24494716","annotations":[{"name":"Pressure","weight":0.278664,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pressure"},{"name":"Measurement","weight":0.187046,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Measurement"},{"name":"Hypertension","weight":0.171135,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hypertension"},{"name":"Management","weight":0.166245,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Management"},{"name":"Blood pressure","weight":0.0633182,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Blood_pressure"},{"name":"Observational study","weight":0.0549849,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Observational_study"},{"name":"Blood","weight":0.0494293,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Blood"},{"name":"Hemodialysis","weight":0.0329831,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hemodialysis"},{"name":"Observation","weight":0.0311179,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Observation"},{"name":"Matter","weight":0.0280659,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Matter"},{"name":"Debate","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Debate"},{"name":"Voluntary association","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Voluntary_association"}]}
